National Media stake held by Joseph Harrosh . Fremont , Calif . , investor Joseph Harrosh said Friday he holds a 5 . 57 percent stake or 1 , 391 , 600 shares in National Media Corp , a Philadelphia - based producer of infomercials . In a filing with the U . S . Securities and Exchange Commission , Harrosh said he acquired the shares between Feb . 24 and Aug . 6 . He most recently purchase was 242 , 500 shares on August 6 at $ 6 . 80 each . Harrosh said he holds the shares for investment " because the shares appear to be substantially undervalued . " 
